                    "value": "passive"
                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": null
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>This curse affects only humanoids</p>\n<p><strong>Saving Throw</strong> @Check[type:fortitude|dc:15].</p>\n<p>On each full moon, the cursed creature must succeed at another Fortitude save or turn into a wearboar until dawn. The creature is under the GM's control and goes on a rampage for half the night before falling unconscious until dawn.</p>"
